name: Experiment Or Die #21
description: Yearlong project to create a new collage every day using my years of photos and personal assets. I interned in NYC in the early Winter of 2006 and while I was there I fell ass backwards into the world of Designer Toys. It started with Kidrobot and evolved to a whole world of amazing figures that had a lush and broad history. 15 years later and I'm still collecting toys and I couldn't even tell you how many I have. IG: Nikejerk
